The string "cabc" will have the same answer as "cab". Similarly, for the string "dcabc" the answer should be same as "dcab".

Now, considering the string "cabca", here you need to check whether the cost for "cabc" + "a" is lesser or cost for "c" + "abca" 

# Approach
