- Note that can be two other turns in a turn, ex: aaabaaaaddaaaa (1 turn a and 1 turn b and 1 turn d), so in this example, the subdevided problem can be: f(aaabaaaaddaaa) = f(abada) = f(aba) + f(ada) - 1.

# Approach
